---
title: Pizza Burgers with Wedges and Salad
description: Pizza burgers! They're officially 'A Thing' and we couldn't be happier about it. Even if you're not good at maths, you know that Pizza + Burger = Double Deliciousness. Our top tip is to add a tiny, tiny splash of water to the  pan to help the cheese melt perfectly. Enjoy!
